prompts.frontCover: Flat 2D illustration for a greeting card. A humorous and dreamy fantasy beach scene featuring the cartoon illustrated versions of Lao Lao and Jordan from the reference photo. Lao Lao is front and center, joyfully riding a giant, majestic sea turtle like a noble steed through the shallow, sparkling turquoise water. She has a wide, happy smile and holds sparkly reigns made of woven seaweed. Jordan is running alongside in the water, looking comically out of breath and flustered as he tries to keep up, holding a beautifully decorated birthday cake high above the water to keep it dry. The sea turtle wears a small, festive party hat at a jaunty angle. The beach has pastel pink sand, and the sky is a magical twilight blend of lavender and soft orange with whimsical, swirling clouds and a few glowing stars. In the background, palm trees have glowing fairy lights strung between them. In the center of the card, written in a beautiful, readable handwritten cursive script, is the text "Happy Birthday Lao Lao". The overall style is ethereal, magical, and playful.
